    h2 Stepper Events
    p Stepper will fire the following DOM events on stepper element and events on app and stepper instance:
    h3 DOM Events
    table.events-table
      thead
        tr
          th Event
          th Target
          th Description
      tbody
        tr
          td stepper:change
          td Stepper Element<span>&lt;div class="stepper"&gt;</span>
          td Event will be triggered when Stepper value has been changed
        tr
          td stepper:beforedestroy
          td Stepper Element<span>&lt;div class="stepper"&gt;</span>
          td Event will be triggered right before Stepper instance will be destroyed
    h3 App and Stepper Instance Events
    p Stepper instance emits events on both self instance and app instance. App instance events has same names prefixed with `stepper`.
    table.events-table.double-events-table
      thead
        tr
